Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.65,0:00:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.65,0:00:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}讓你久等了 綾斗 真是千鈞一髮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.97,0:00:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}克勞蒂雅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.61,0:00:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}尤莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.57,0:00:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}孤毒魔女...奧菲莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.73,0:00:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}對了 在那之後我失去了意識
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.25,0:00:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.09,0:00:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你終於醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.21,0:00:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}尤莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.93,0:00:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.33,0:00:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你整整昏迷了三天 我很擔心你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.21,0:00:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}三天?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.41,0:00:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}她們倆也非常擔心你 每天都陪在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.45,0:00:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}之後好好犒勞一下她們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.57,0:01:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}另外...我也還沒有向你道謝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.17,0:01:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}道謝?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.33,0:01:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我聽說當時不只奧菲莉亞 連古斯塔夫都出現了對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.41,0:01:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}抱歉 多虧你救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.05,0:01:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}沒關係啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.69,0:01:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}事到如今 你應該也不會說欠我一個人情之類的話了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.49,0:01:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不是 我只是想把這份謝意明確地告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.57,0:01:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那麼 能不能告訴我呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.21,0:01:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}尤莉絲你和她...奧菲莉亞· 蘭朵露芬之間的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.13,0:01:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你還記得這個吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.01,0:01:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}當然
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.45,0:01:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我記得是孤兒院的大家在上面刺了繡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.33,0:01:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}然後還是尤莉絲的一位好朋友縫的手帕...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.49,0:01:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}她不擅長和別人爭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.89,0:01:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}真的是一個很善良的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.49,0:01:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}難道說...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.65,0:01:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}沒錯 縫製這條手帕的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.41,0:02:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}就是奧菲莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.43,0:03:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}做這種事情到底哪裏有趣了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.03,0:03:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}植物啊 是一種非常正直的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.15,0:03:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}只要對它們投入愛 它們就會回應你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.23,0:03:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}相反 一旦疏於照顧 它們就會拋棄你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.43,0:03:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}拋棄? 植物會拋棄人?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.79,0:03:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那些沒有得病的植物會枯萎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.67,0:04:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}是因為對人類感到厭惡的關係哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.75,0:04:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}她是一個最喜歡照顧植物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.59,0:04:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}連一條蟲都不敢殺的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.71,0:04:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}唯有美麗的花朵綻放時 會表現得比較愉快活潑一點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.19,0:04:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那...昨天她那種樣子是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.43,0:04:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}昨天我們去的那片雪原的廢墟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.59,0:04:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}是奧菲莉亞力量失控所導致的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.67,0:04:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那裏以前是統合企業財體聖母之索的研究設施
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.91,0:04:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}一位被稱為「大博士」的阿爾坎特的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.03,0:04:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}在那裏進行著某項研究
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.15,0:04:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}研究內容是...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.63,0:04:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}創造出後天的「星脈世代」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.19,0:04:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}拿來當試驗品的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.79,0:04:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}就是為了抵押孤兒院的鉅額債務而被徵集的...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.87,0:04:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}奧菲莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.47,0:05:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}結果...本來連「星脈世代」都不是的奧菲莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.55,0:05:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}如今卻成了世界最強的「魔女」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.15,0:05:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這麼說 研究成功了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.51,0:05:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.71,0:05:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那片廢墟的地面被持續腐蝕 如今依舊寸草不生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.95,0:05:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}作為獲得力量的代價
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.83,0:05:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}曾經那般熱愛的花朵 她甚至連靠近都做不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.83,0:05:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}在六芒星再度見到她時 她完全變了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.11,0:05:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}彷彿對過去對自已完全死心 全部捨棄了一般
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.11,0:05:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你之前和她正面交鋒過 應該能感受得到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.47,0:05:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}奧菲莉亞那強大到異常的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.87,0:05:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}是一把愈使用就愈會腐蝕自身的雙刃劍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.12,0:05:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我很想阻止她 不要再亂來了 可是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.12,0:06:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}結果 不用說你也知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.08,0:06:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}很抱歉 這次把你也捲了進來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.36,0:06:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}但接下來的事 我必須獨自去完成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.20,0:06:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不然 奧菲莉亞她也無法接受的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.08,0:06:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.72,0:06:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}事情就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.88,0:06:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}還有在那邊裝睡的兩個傢伙 也拜託你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.72,0:06:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你發現了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.32,0:06:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.72,0:06:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}算了 比起那個 現在得優先對付古斯塔夫·馬爾洛才行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.44,0:06:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}難道那之後又遭到什麼人的襲擊了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.08,0:06:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不 這點倒不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.96,0:06:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}首都全域都已經提高了警戒等級 警備力度大幅增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.76,0:06:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}以防萬一 孤兒院那邊也派人加強戒備了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.08,0:07:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}要是那傢伙敢出現的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.68,0:07:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不不不...不得了啦 公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.56,0:07:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}芙羅拉!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.52,0:07:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}怎麼了? 幹嘛慌慌張張的?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.92,0:07:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}是...是的 城裏好像發生不得了的大事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.44,0:07:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}聽說出現了好多這麼大的像礫蠍一樣的東西在天上飛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.24,0:07:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那些東西有襲擊人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.40,0:07:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不 這倒沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.56,0:07:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}警備人員們已經全體出動 正在應對這種情況
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.40,0:07:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}目前似乎還沒有出現大的損失
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.72,0:07:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}什麼 你說全體出動?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.64,0:07:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這麼說 孤兒院的警備隊也
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.24,0:07:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}是的 聽說警備隊的各位也前往城裏了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.44,0:07:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}尤莉絲 冷靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}古斯塔夫他很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.96,0:07:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這個國家的警備隊根本不會重視孤兒院那種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.60,0:07:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}以及 這是一個把我們引出來的絕佳誘餌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.88,0:08:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那傢伙肯定正在貧民街等著我們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.68,0:08:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}並且 如果我不出現 他肯定會將孤兒院
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.64,0:08:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這是我的問題 你們不要跟過來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.44,0:08:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}事到如今你還在說 什麼啊 尤莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.56,0:08:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}就是呀 因為被盯上的人並不只有尤莉絲學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.84,0:08:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這次我們也是當事者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.92,0:08:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.84,0:08:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那麼 我現在有一個方案
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.24,0:08:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}能請你們按我說的行動嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.44,0:08:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}古斯塔夫· 馬爾洛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.16,0:08:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}幸會幸會 尤莉絲王女殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.00,0:09:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}勞煩您來這種地方 我真是不勝惶恐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.08,0:09:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你還沒有對孤兒院出手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.72,0:09:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}請放心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.92,0:09:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}要是在釣上獵物之前就把重要的誘餌摧毀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.48,0:09:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那可就沒有意義了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.44,0:09:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}首先 我得把諸位請出來才行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.72,0:09:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這東西是...許德拉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.40,0:09:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}您說的一點兒沒錯 王女殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.00,0:09:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這姿態就跟神話中描述的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.92,0:09:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不 比神話中描述的更為雄壯威猛吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.00,0:09:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}好了 既然已經把獵物吸引出來了 那誘餌也就沒用了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.04,0:09:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}趕緊結束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.64,0:10:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那麼我就先失陪了 請兩位盡情享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.92,0:10:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}站住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.04,0:10:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}尤莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.16,0:10:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}抱歉 綾斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.60,0:10:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不 比起這個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.28,0:10:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.44,0:10:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}意思是要保護城鎮的話 就得先阻止它嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.28,0:10:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}現在警備隊還沒有來 就只能靠我們想辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.88,0:10:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}尤莉絲 引導居民們避難的工作就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.00,0:10:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}難道你要一個人去阻止那玩意嗎!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.32,0:10:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}而且 紗夜她們應該也差不多準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.20,0:10:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}可 是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.12,0:10:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}尤莉絲你比較熟悉這一帶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.84,0:10:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}而且鎮上的大家也更願意聽你的話不是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.44,0:10:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.88,0:10:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}但是你可千萬不要亂來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.88,0:10:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}沒有弄錯吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.00,0:10:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}有需要的話我把我這邊掌握到的證據給你傳過去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.36,0:11:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不 這個就不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.64,0:11:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不能再讓它為所欲為了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.56,0:11:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}在這裏擋住它
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.88,0:11:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}連再生都和神話裏描述的一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.76,0:11:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}綾斗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.96,0:11:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}久等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.86,0:12:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}謝謝你 紗夜 得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.26,0:12:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這個像蛇一樣的東西就是目標?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.38,0:12:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}作戰方案呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.06,0:12:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}古斯塔夫對再現神話極為執著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.14,0:12:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這樣的話 在砍掉中央那顆頭顱之前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.50,0:12:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}就算打倒周圍的頭顱 也會立刻再生出來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.90,0:12:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}也就是說要用速攻?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.58,0:12:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}沒錯 拜託你一直開著視窗別關哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.18,0:12:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}OK  那麼 儘管上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.50,0:12:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}先砍掉兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.70,0:12:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}4點方向
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.94,0:13:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}四個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.90,0:13:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}6點方向 交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.14,0:13:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這樣就六個了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.30,0:13:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}紗夜 下一擊決勝負吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.18,0:13:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.26,0:13:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}天霧辰明流
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.14,0:13:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}貳蛟龍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.42,0:13:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這麼一來就只剩下一個了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.06,0:13:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}綾斗 3 點方向
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.10,0:13:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}集中在一顆頭顱上 加快了再生速度嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.78,0:13:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}還沒完
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.74,0:14:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你們兩個都做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.90,0:14:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我這邊也設定完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.26,0:14:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}綻放吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.70,0:14:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}大輪爆耀華...二輪開
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.90,0:15:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}哎呀呀 真是傷腦筋了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.02,0:15:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你怎麼會猜到我在這裏?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.94,0:15:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}像你這種型別的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.86,0:15:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}肯定會挑一個能將貧民街一覽無餘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.78,0:15:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}並且安全又距離不遠的地方觀察戰況
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.54,0:15:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這是尤莉絲小姐的看法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.86,0:15:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}原來如此 真是一群聰明得令人生厭的小姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.54,0:15:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我是綺凜 已經抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.18,0:15:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}父親
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.34,0:15:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}古斯塔夫· 馬爾洛已經抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.46,0:15:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我們也好久沒見面了啊 克勞蒂雅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.06,0:15:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}銀河的人僱傭罪犯襲擊星導館的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.82,0:16:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}並且還是一國的王女
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.50,0:16:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}和銀河沒關係 這是我個人策劃的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.58,0:16:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}以父親的立場而言 是沒法用這種藉口開脫的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.38,0:16:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我認為母親也做出了這種判斷吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.70,0:16:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}估計是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.90,0:16:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}她只要認為有必要 我這種人便能夠輕易地捨棄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.14,0:16:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}也就是說 這次的事情對你們而言並沒有任何用處
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.70,0:16:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.90,0:16:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你應該知道真到了那時會變成什麼情況吧 克勞蒂雅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.74,0:16:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}即便如此 你依舊要參加「獅鷲星武祭」的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.62,0:16:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}拜託你 至少換一個願望吧 現在還來得及
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.14,0:16:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我應該和您說過很多次了 這個我也辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我...我其實很愛你的啊 克勞蒂雅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.66,0:16:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}父親為我做的事情 我真的很感激
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.66,0:17:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那麼 再會了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.10,0:17:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}真的是給各位添了諸多麻煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.26,0:17:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}多虧了你們 我國又恢復了太平
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.34,0:17:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}國民們也非常感謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.78,0:17:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}特別是尤莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.70,0:17:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}老城區的人們 說不定要再為你舉行一次遊行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.02,0:17:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這樣下去就會讓皇兄失去立足之地...嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.54,0:17:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那麼 皇兄 趁此機會就讓我把話挑明了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.58,0:17:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你想說什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.74,0:17:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我要奪得「獅鷲星武祭」的冠軍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.14,0:17:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}然後擴大萊澤塔尼亞國王的許可權
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.66,0:17:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}通過這次的事情讓我確信了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.02,0:17:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}若要改變這個國家 就必須從更加根本的部分上下手才行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.44,0:17:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}確實 作為「星武祭」的獎賞 是可以擴大王權的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.48,0:17:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}如此一來 就會給皇兄帶來負擔和麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.56,0:18:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}但即便如此我還是要拜託你 皇兄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.16,0:18:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你能不能助我一臂之力?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.40,0:18:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}尤莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.56,0:18:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你真的變了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.40,0:18:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}沒想到竟然會有來拜託我的一天啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.96,0:18:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這也是受天霧君...不 是受了你們各位的影響嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.00,0:18:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我知道了 尤莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.12,0:18:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我向你保證
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.80,0:18:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}如果你真的成功稱霸了「獅鷲星武祭」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.16,0:18:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那我到時候也下定決心脫離廢人好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.20,0:18:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}皇兄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.88,0:18:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.92,0:18:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}真是一對好兄妹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.80,0:18:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}確實
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.12,0:18:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}運營委員長!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.76,0:18:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}天霧君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.92,0:18:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我們找到你姐姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.96,0:19:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}姐姐...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.68,0:19:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你姐姐天霧遙大約在五年前被送來了這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.20,0:19:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}據說從那個時候開始 她的身體便處於假死狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.12,0:19:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}一直到今天 都沒有出現過任何變化
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.44,0:19:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}據猜測這可能是某種能力帶來的作用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.80,0:19:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}聽醫師說 目前似乎沒有任何辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.16,0:19:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這大概是姐姐自身的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.32,0:19:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}能把一切事物封禁起來的禁獄之力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.64,0:19:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不知道是什麼原因 姐姐對自己施加了這一能力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.72,0:19:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}如果這種狀態一直持續下去 會不會有生命危險呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.24,0:19:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}如果這種狀態一直持續的話 據說會比你要長壽得多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.00,0:19:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}前提是 如果這樣能算是「活著」的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.16,0:20:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}聽說你姐姐好像找到了呢 天霧綾斗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.68,0:20:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我可以治好你姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.20,0:20:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你...究竟是什麼人?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.00,0:20:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我是希兒妲瞿珍·羅蘭茲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.64,0:20:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}阿爾坎特研究院「超人派」會長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.16,0:20:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}大家都稱呼我為
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.24,0:20:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}「大博士」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.04,0:20:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}請允許我再次道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.48,0:20:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}在萊澤塔尼亞的時候 家父給大家帶來了很大的麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.04,0:20:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}可是 為什麼會長的父親要委託那種事呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.08,0:20:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}因為如果我奪得「獅鷲星武祭」冠軍的話會很麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.68,0:20:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}其實不是我父親 應該說是銀河才對
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.80,0:20:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}可是 這樣的話應該還有其它辦法吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.68,0:20:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}父親是希望在銀河動真格之前 想辦法搞定這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.20,0:21:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}因為父親很清楚 一旦他們動起真格來 我會有什麼下場...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.92,0:21:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你知不知道自己在說什麼啊?
